ActTerritorial Lands Act
PrecisWITHDRAWAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (NAHANNI NATIONAL PARK RESERVE OF CANADA) FROM DISPOSAL ORDER - which provides for the withdrawal from disposal of certain lands (28,800 km²) located in the Northwest Territories until October 31, 2008, in order facilitate the expansion of the Nahanni National Park Reserve of Canada.
